title: Ep. - 553 - LOVE IS BLIND 3 WITH CHRIS DEROSA REAL HOUSEWIVES OF BEVERLY HILLS REUNION PART 2
description:
Kate discusses part 2 of the Real Housewives of Beverly Hills reunion.

 

Reality TV producer Chris DeRosa helps Kate review Love is Blind 3, a social experiment where single men and women look for love and get engaged, all before meeting in person. The Netflix series is based this season in Dallas.
